{
  "text": "The updating algorithm used for sampling the path integral is Metropolis-Hastings one, consisting of a set of local moves (see Ref. [5, [CITATION_1] for more details). In all simulations we used N t = 80 spatial slices, keeping the total spatial volume V S,tot fluctuating around a fixed target volume by tuning one of the bare parameters (k 4 ).",
